This paper discusses the vulnerabilities of privacy infrastructures, which is a topic related to computer security (cs.CR) and network security (cs.NI). It also touches on the use of botnets and Tor, which are topics related to cybercrime (cs.CY). The analysis of vulnerabilities may involve software engineering (cs.SE) and system integration (cs.SI) as well.
